title: Young Dolph Shot At Over 100 Times [VIDEO]
text:
Young Dolph Shot At Over 100 Times [VIDEO] posted by @ACThePlug - 
Rapper Young Dolph was the alleged target of over 100 shots fired at on North Caldwell Street outside The Spectrum Center where the CIAA weekend events are taking place. 
Reports say the rapper came out clean as the SUV he was riding in was bulletproof. 
While no injuries have been reported, multiple cars and nearby apartment buildings were hit several times. 
The motive for the shooting at this time is unclear. 
A video of the aftermath has surfaced. Check it out below. A post shared by DOLPH GABANNA (@youngdolph) on Feb 26, 2017 at 12:14am PST 
Photo: Getty Images
